name: Analog Journey - Tryptocoin
description: "Analog Journey is a small collection of simulated chiptunes, made with "Analog" instrument on Ableton. It is the synthesis of my path, my story and my feelings, presented to you in 8 bits. Tryptocoin was originally called "Peaceful Gunner' in tribute to my university teatcher, Suami 'KomBits'Abdalla." Created by Pedro Kozovits A.K.A Fractal Vector. Personal, non-commercial use only.
